cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.NA, cs.OC. 

The paper proposes a new method for selecting coordinates in coordinate descent methods, which are commonly used in optimization problems in machine learning and data science. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves numerical optimization, which could fall under cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), and the use of a multi-armed bandit algorithm, which could fall under cs.OC (Optimization and Control).
